@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Active
Active --> OnHold : process
OnHold --> Delivered : review
OnHold : entry / log catalog
Delivered --> Completed : process
Completed --> Archived : review
Archived --> [*]
@enduml